o enter UH.  To find out more about public transportation and parking on campus, please visit the UIC Parking & Transportation page.  To find out more about getting to UIC, please visit the UIC Directions page.       OIA Information  509 University Hall (M/C 590) 601 South Morgan Street Chicago, IL 60607-7128  P: 312-996-5455 F: 312-413-7857 E: oia@uic.edu   News News at OIA            Â© Copyright 2014-2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois      Footer Navigation   University of Illinois Hospital & Health Sciences System Fulbright Google Translate Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Privacy Policy  Contact Us           Cookie Settings   